{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 365, "title": "Increase battle damage to shorten fights", "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThis change starts work on Issue #197 by increasing battle damage so fights do not take as long.\r\n\r\n## Changes made\r\n\r\n* updated the `get_hp(...)` calculation in `src/pokete/classes/fight/attack_process.py`\r\n* kept missed attacks at `0`\r\n* added a minimum damage floor of `4` for landed attacks\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n\r\n* tested locally first on my own branch/fork\r\n* confirmed battles felt noticeably faster\r\n* pushed the branch to the group fork for review and testing before merging\r\n", "baseRefName": "master", "baseRefOid": "bb9a07d98644be489f918e9a67d4ca081135a434", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "lxgr-linux/pokete"}, "url": "https://github.com/lxgr-linux/pokete/pull/365", "createdAt": "2026-04-27T11:51:36Z", "mergedAt": "2026-04-27T21:32:23Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "lxgr-linux/pokete"}, "sha": "bb9a07d98644be489f918e9a67d4ca081135a434"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/lxgr-linux/pokete/pull/365.diff", "number": 365, "created_at": "2026-04-27T11:51:36Z", "merged_at": "2026-04-27T21:32:23Z", "resolved_issues": [197]}
